high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the counter, then hang a right and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the small metal spoon out of the sink.
Turn around and walk forward, then hang a right and walk up to the counter and look down at the lower cabinets.
Open the lower cabinets below the counter and put the spoon into the bowl that is in the cabinet.
Pick up the bowl with the spoon in it and close the cabinet door.
Walk back over to the kitchen sink.
Put the bowl with the spoon in it into the sink in front of the egg.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a spoon in it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk across the room, to the sink on the right.
Remove the spoon in front of the apples, inside the sink.
Turn to the cabinets, underneath the counter to your right.
Place the spoon in the bowl, inside the cabinets.
Remove the bowl with the spoon inside it, from the kitchen cabinets.
Turn back to the kitchen sink, to your right.
Place the bowl with the spoon inside in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl containing a spoon inside the sink.

high_descs: Turn right, move down to the sink on the right.
Pick up the spoon in the sink.
Bring the spoon to the left, to the bottom cabinet right of the stove.
Open that cabinet, put the spoon in the bowl in that cabinet.
Pick up the bowl with spoon from in the cabinet.
Bring the bowl to the sink on the right.
Put the bowl with spoon in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a spoon in it, in the sink.
